<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>Your Fizzy account <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> has been scheduled for deletion.</p>

<h2>What happens now?</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Your account is now suspended</strong> – No one can access it anymore</li>
  <li><strong>Your subscription has been paused</strong> – You won't be charged</li>
  <li><strong>Deletion date:</strong> <%= @deletion_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> (<%= @days_remaining %> days from now)</li>
</ul>

<h2>What will be deleted?</h2>

<p>After <%= @days_remaining %> days, all of your account data will be permanently deleted:</p>

<ul>
  <li>All boards and cards</li>
  <li>All comments and attachments</li>
  <li>All user accounts and settings</li>
  <li>All webhooks and integrations</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>This action cannot be undone.</strong></p>

<h2>Changed your mind?</h2>

<p>If you want to cancel this deletion and restore your account, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@fizzy.do">support@fizzy.do</a> before <%= @deletion_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>The Fizzy Team</p>
